@Anonymous
LOL. We've got some science-y commentators here but be forewarned, we also have those with PT(h)SD -- post-traumatHic stress disorder. They will run screaming from anything equation-like, shrieking as they flee: "I was told there would be no maths." Gentle handling is advised.
Welcome and feel free to drop in with questions and comments. Don't worry about speed-solving. Enjoy the puzzle.

@Marlene

Puzzle drops early on Saturday and Sunday.

I finished my first Saturday by accidentally thinking it was a Friday.

@Fleur Anne

Son of a gun! YES, it's the Sunday puzzle...didn't realize it but I should have because I did it so quickly. Luckily, there's still time for me to sweat over the Saturday!

My first weekend puzzles since I'm back from vacation, so I forgive myself. Thanks, friends!

