I've only visited the PNW once, for my friend's wedding in autumn, 1999. It was gorgeous weather the entire week I was there save one, when it was overcast but not rainy. (My friend said that's why they chose to get married at that time of year.) I had a great trip and always thought I'd be back... Not yet! She still lives in Portland, though. If she weren't back East so regularly I'd have made it out there by now — but never say never! 

... I loved Throwing Muses back in the day, and Garbage after that. I never thought of a connection, but I can totally see it!

